com.mobius.vdrapi
Interface IHasTopicItemEntryInfo

All Known Implementing Classes:
TopicItemEntryNode
public interface IHasTopicItemEntryInfo

A class implements IHasTopicItemEntryInfo to indicate that it has information defining a topic item entry.

The methods in this interface can be used to retrieve the information for the topic item entry.

Method Summary
 long getArchiveOriginalPageNumber()
          Returns the physical page number in the original report - namely, the report from which the report archive was created, and to which the topic item refers.
 long getArchivePageRBA()
          Returns the page RBA number for the first page in the topic item.
 Availability getAvailability()
          Returns the availability code of the report archive version containing the topic item.
 DeviceCode getDeviceCode()
          Returns the device location code of the report archive version containing the topic item.
 long getNumberOfPages()
          Returns the number of contiguous report archive pages to which the topic item refers.
 String getReportId()
          Returns the ID of the report containing the topic item.
 String getSectionName()
          Returns the qualified section ID of the report archive page to which the topic item refers.
 String getTopicItemName()
          Returns the topic item name for this topic item entry.
 String getVersionId()
          Returns the Version ID of the report containing the topic item.
